Class PSAM_qcom

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rscja.team.qcom.deviceapi.Device_qcom
      • com.rscja.team.qcom.deviceapi.PSAM_qcom
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPSAM

    public class PSAM_qcom
extends Device_qcom
implements IPSAM
    PSAM操作类
    PSAM operation type

    注意：
    Attention:
    1、使用前请确认您的机器已安装此模块。
    1. Make sure this module is installed before using your device.
    2、要正常使用模块需要在\libs\armeabi\目录放置libDeviceAPI.so文件
    2. Put libDeviceAPI.so file in directory \libs\armeabi\ then module can be used normally.
    3、在操作设备前需要调用 init() 打开设备，使用完后调用 free() 关闭设备 3. Call init() to switch on device before operating the device, call free() to switch off device after using.

    Author:
    liuruifeng
